public class PersonalizableObjectCM
extends org.apache.myfaces.trinidad.model.CollectionModel

A collectionModel based off a List of sparse PersonalizableObjects, using isActive to determine whether a row is surfaced in the CollectionModel.

downOne

public void downOne(int index)
Move the item at 0 based index index (based ONLY on active objects) down one. This method will not range check, trying to move the last item down will throw an Exception.

Parameters:
index - 0 based index of active item to move down.

upOne

public void upOne(int index)
Move the item at 0 based index index (based ONLY on active objects) up one, that is it should be higer in the list than it was before. This method will not range check, trying to move the first item up will throw an Exception.

Parameters:
index - 0 based index of active item to move up.
